text: == Events == * Russia breaks 60 year old truce with Sweden by attacking Finland * February 2 – Diet of Augsburg begins * February 4 – John Rogers becomes first Protestant martyr in England * February 9 – Bishop of Gloucester John Hooper is burned at the stake * May 23 – Paul IV becomes Pope. * September 25 – Peace of Augsburg is signed. == Births == * * == Deaths == * *
